{"id":5448,"date":"2023-05-29T17:17:46","date_gmt":"2023-05-29T17:17:46","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.screeningdate.com\/?p=5448"},"modified":"2024-03-30T17:23:13","modified_gmt":"2024-03-30T17:23:13","slug":"chevening-scholarships-in-botswana","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/chevening-scholarships-in-botswana\/","title":{"rendered":"Apply for Botswana Chevening Scholarships 2024"},"content":{"rendered":"<p><strong><em>Chevening Scholarships in Botswana 2024, Eligibility criteria, required\u00a0 documents to be submitted, selection updates and timelines, How to apply.<\/em><br \/>\n<\/strong><\/p><div id=\"ez-toc-container\" class=\"ez-toc-v2_0_64 ez-toc-wrap-center counter-hierarchy ez-toc-counter ez-toc-light-blue ez-toc-container-direction\">\n<div class=\"ez-toc-title-container\">\n<p class=\"ez-toc-title \" >Contents on This Page<\/p>\n<span class=\"ez-toc-title-toggle\"><a href=\"#\" class=\"ez-toc-pull-right ez-toc-btn ez-toc-btn-xs ez-toc-btn-default ez-toc-toggle\" aria-label=\"Toggle Table of Content\"><span class=\"ez-toc-js-icon-con\"><span class=\"\"><span class=\"eztoc-hide\" style=\"display:none;\">Toggle<\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-icon-toggle-span\"><svg style=\"fill: #999;color:#999\" xmlns=\"http:\/\/www.w3.org\/2000\/svg\" class=\"list-377408\" width=\"20px\" height=\"20px\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\"><path d=\"M6 6H4v2h2V6zm14 0H8v2h12V6zM4 11h2v2H4v-2zm16 0H8v2h12v-2zM4 16h2v2H4v-2zm16 0H8v2h12v-2z\" fill=\"currentColor\"><\/path><\/svg><svg style=\"fill: #999;color:#999\" class=\"arrow-unsorted-368013\" xmlns=\"http:\/\/www.w3.org\/2000\/svg\" width=\"10px\" height=\"10px\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" version=\"1.2\" baseProfile=\"tiny\"><path d=\"M18.2 9.3l-6.2-6.3-6.2 6.3c-.2.2-.3.4-.3.7s.1.5.3.7c.2.2.4.3.7.3h11c.3 0 .5-.1.7-.3.2-.2.3-.5.3-.7s-.1-.5-.3-.7zM5.8 14.7l6.2 6.3 6.2-6.3c.2-.2.3-.5.3-.7s-.1-.5-.3-.7c-.2-.2-.4-.3-.7-.3h-11c-.3 0-.5.1-.7.3-.2.2-.3.5-.3.7s.1.5.3.7z\"\/><\/svg><\/span><\/span><\/span><\/a><\/span><\/div>\n<nav><ul class='ez-toc-list ez-toc-list-level-1 eztoc-toggle-hide-by-default' ><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-1\" href=\"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/chevening-scholarships-in-botswana\/#About_the_Botswana_Chevening_Scholarship\" title=\"About the Botswana Chevening Scholarship\">About the Botswana Chevening Scholarship<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-2\" href=\"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/chevening-scholarships-in-botswana\/#Eligibility_by_criteria_for_Botswana_Chevening_Scholarship\" title=\"Eligibility by criteria for Botswana Chevening Scholarship\">Eligibility by criteria for Botswana Chevening Scholarship<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-3\" href=\"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/chevening-scholarships-in-botswana\/#Required_documents_to_be_submitted\" title=\"Required documents to be submitted\">Required documents to be submitted<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-4\" href=\"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/chevening-scholarships-in-botswana\/#Selection_updates_and_timelines\" title=\"Selection updates\u00a0and timelines\">Selection updates\u00a0and timelines<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-5\" href=\"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/chevening-scholarships-in-botswana\/#How_to_apply_for_Botswana_Chevening_Scholarship\" title=\"How to apply for Botswana Chevening Scholarship\">How to apply for Botswana Chevening Scholarship<\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/nav><\/div>\n\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-medium wp-image-5452 aligncenter\" src=\"https:\/\/www.applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/10\/botswana-300x169.jpg\" alt=\"Chevening Scholarships in Botswana 2024\" width=\"300\" height=\"169\" title=\"\"><\/p>\n<p><strong>Applications for 2024 Chevening Scholarships are now open.<\/strong><\/p>\n<p><strong>Scholarship Deadline<\/strong>: 2 November 2024 (Open for applications until 2 November 2024, at 12:00 (GMT).<\/p>\n<p><strong>Contents<\/strong><\/p>\n<p><a href=\"#_Toc86377487\">Brief<\/a><\/p>\n<p><a href=\"#_Toc86377488\">Eligibility criteria<\/a><\/p>\n<p><a href=\"#_Toc86377489\">Required documents to be submitted<\/a><\/p>\n<p><a href=\"#_Toc86377490\">Selection updates\u00a0and timelines<\/a><\/p>\n<p><a href=\"#_Toc86377491\">How to apply<\/a><\/p>\n<h2 id=\"about-the-botswana-chevening-scholarship\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"About_the_Botswana_Chevening_Scholarship\"><\/span><a name=\"_Toc86377487\"><\/a>About the Botswana Chevening Scholarship<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>Chevening is the UK government\u2019s international scholarships programme. It is funded by the Foreign, Commonwealth and Development Office and partner organizations; we offer awards to study in the UK for one year on a fully funded master\u2019s degree course.<\/p>\n<p>All Successful Chevening candidates come from a diverse range of countries and backgrounds, but they all show the passion, vision and skills needed to shape a better world.<\/p>\n<p>There are a lot of benefits to being preferred, as well as completely funded tuition fees, access to some of the best quality education in the world, exclusive networking opportunities, and the opportunity to explore the UK\u2019s diverse culture.<\/p>\n<p>At the end of your scholarship, you\u2019ll join our diverse community of over 50,000 global alumni. You\u2019ll return home prepared with the knowledge and networks to bring your ideas to life and succeed in your career.<\/p>\n<p>It doesn\u2019t matter where you come from. It\u2019s where you\u2019re going that counts.<\/p>\n<h2 id=\"eligibility-by-criteria-for-botswana-chevening-scholarship\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Eligibility_by_criteria_for_Botswana_Chevening_Scholarship\"><\/span><a name=\"_Toc86377488\"><\/a>Eligibility by criteria for Botswana Chevening Scholarship<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>It is open to all nationals it does not matter where your tribe.<\/p>\n<h2 id=\"required-documents-to-be-submitted\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Required_documents_to_be_submitted\"><\/span><a name=\"_Toc86377489\"><\/a>Required documents to be submitted<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>Please note that All Chevening applicants must present their education documents, references, and one unconditional UK university offer. The time limits for these mandatory documents are in the\u00a0<strong><a href=\"https:\/\/www.chevening.org\/scholarships\/application-timeline\/\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Chevening application timeline<\/a><\/strong>. Use the \u2018update my application\u2019 button above to upload them.<\/p>\n<p>If you are conditionally chosen for a Chevening Scholarship, it is necessary to you forward these documents in order to continue in the progression.<\/p>\n<h2 id=\"selection-updates-and-timelines\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Selection_updates_and_timelines\"><\/span><a name=\"_Toc86377490\"><\/a>Selection updates\u00a0and timelines<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>After applying you will receive an email updates regarding your application status at each step of the selection process. You can as well confirm your status on the online application system.<\/p>\n<h2 id=\"how-to-apply-for-botswana-chevening-scholarship\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"How_to_apply_for_Botswana_Chevening_Scholarship\"><\/span><a name=\"_Toc86377491\"><\/a>How to apply for Botswana Chevening Scholarship<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>Log in using your registration details. Take a look at the\u00a0<a href=\"https:\/\/www.chevening.org\/apply\/application-timeline\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Chevening application timeline<\/a>\u00a0\u00a0for a better understanding of the upcoming stages of the selection process.<\/p>\n<p><em><strong>See also&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;<\/strong><\/em><a title=\"Coca-Cola Scholarship Foundation\" href=\"https:\/\/www.applyjobs.org.ng\/coca-cola-scholarship-foundation\/\" rel=\"bookmark nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Coca-Cola Scholarship Foundation<\/strong><\/a><\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"Chevening Scholarships in Botswana 2024, Eligibility criteria, required\u00a0 documents to be submitted, selection updates and timelines, How to&hellip;\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":14931,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"footnotes":""},"categories":[14],"tags":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/5448"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=5448"}],"version-history":[{"count":1,"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/5448\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":19292,"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/5448\/revisions\/19292"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/14931"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=5448"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=5448"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=